title: Daytona USA ROM (Model 2)
description:
This is the ROM dump for Daytona USA for the Model 2 arcade system.

It seems that a working version of this is almost impossible to find anywhere on the net, so I fixed a broken version of the ROM dump by inserting the missing files from other Model 2 ROM dumps, and decided to host it here.

You&#039;ll need a Model 2 emulator to run these files.

Enjoy!
